Dga cho'en dill' nan Jesucrístona' nake' xiiṉ dia c̱he dii Davina' na' dii Abrahama'.
―¿Gaṉi rey c̱he beṉ' Israelka', bi'na' ba golj? Ṉezinto' ba goljb' ḻa' ka de gana' chla'lə wbilla' ble'into' to belj dii bzajniin neto' nan ba goljb', daan ba za'nto' kwenc̱he we'la'onto'b'.
Na' ka billingake' Galileana' jazoagake' yell Nazareta'. Na' daa jazoagake' na', gok ka wna dii beṉ'ka' wdix̱jee daa goll Chioza' ḻegake' kani'yi c̱he Jesúza', wnagake' wsi'gake'ne' beṉ' Nazaret.
Na'ch goll Jesúza':
Na'ch Jesúza' chi'e ḻegake':
Per nad' nia' le', nottez beena' chllee bish' ljwelle'na' chidoḻee tie' lo yeḻ' zak'zi'na'. Na' ḻekzka' beena' chzoazi'yee bish' ljwelle'na', beṉ'ka' chṉabia' chiyaḻ' wwiagake' nak gongake' c̱he'; na' beena' chṉie' bish' ljwelle'na' dill' zibia', chidoḻee wzaḻ' Chioza' ḻe' lo yi' gabiḻa'.
San ḻi gaklen beṉ' ka kono gakbe'i. Na' X̱achona', beena' chen chle'i daa chonle, goṉe' laxjle.
Na' shi Chioza' none' yejdo'ka' ze lyix̱aa xochi, ḻa'kzi nakan de toldezə na'tech chtop beṉ' ḻen na' chzeye'n, ¿alechla le', gontechle' wen c̱hele goṉe' xalaanle ḻa'kzi bitek chajḻe'le gaklene' le'?
Per beena' cheni cho'a xtillaani na' bi chone' ka nia', nake' ka beena' bi chajnii, beena' bx̱e lille'na' lo yoxa'.
Gok ka' kwenc̱he gok ka wna dii Isaíaza', beena' wdix̱jee daa goll Chioza'ne', daa wne': “Ḻe' bikee yillwe'ka' che'icho na' bene' ka bigaa yeḻ' chey chla c̱hechona'.”
Na' biyoo Jesúza' to ḻoo barkw, na'ch biḻag'gake' shḻaa nisdo'na' na' billine' yell c̱he'na' gana' wzee.
Na' ka zejgake' lill beṉ' wṉabia'na' jano to noolə ḻegake', na' ba gok shlliṉ yiz chzoe' wbaa. Na'ch wbiguee koll' Jesúza' bex̱ee xe'na',
―Dii ḻi nia' le', beṉ'ka' zi' gonḻilall'gake' Chioza' zaklebgakile' to dii wlliachga to lo yell-lio, na' chyallj no yizi' yilapan, per to c̱hopchga wen llinka' zoa.
Bi illeble beṉ'ka' cheengakile' witgake' le', ḻa' kwerp c̱hele na'zan witgake', aga bi gak gongakile' yic̱hjlall'do'lena'. San Chiozan' chiyaḻ' illeble, ḻa' ḻen' wakə wlliayee kwerp c̱helena' len yic̱hjlall'do'lena' lo yi' gabiḻa'.
Dii ḻi nia' le', ladj yog' beṉ' yell-lioki, ni toe' biṉ' ichej gake' beṉ' zak'chi' aga ka Juanna' beena' chchoa beṉ' nisa'. Per nottezə beena' choe' latj iṉabia' Chioza' yic̱hjlall'do'ena', zak'teche' aga ka Juanna'.
Bilja wyajniile bi zeji Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' daa na: “Nad' cheenchid' yiyeshii ljwell-le, aga ka daa witle bayix̱'ka' kwenc̱he we'la'ole nad'.” Ḻa' sheḻ' le' wyajniilen, aga waole xya c̱he beṉ' bi nap doḻ', sheḻ'ka'.
Na' gokbe'i Jesúza' daa chza'lall' fariseoka', na'ch chi'e ḻegake':
―Beṉ'kin xṉa'na' na' beṉ' bishaaka'.
’Ḻi wzenag bin zeji jempl c̱he beṉ' goz gooṉa'.
Nad', Beṉ' Bseḻ' Chioza' Yell-lioni, wseḻaa anjl c̱ha'ka' kwenc̱he yitopgake' beṉ' wen dii malka' na' beṉ'ka' chzechgake' beṉ' yoblə gongake' dii mala'.
Na' daa golle'ne' ka' goklall' Heródeza' wite'ne', per bi biyaxjile' daa bllebe' beṉ'ka' chajḻe' daa nak Juanna' to beṉ' chyix̱jee daa che' Chioza'ne'.
Na'ch wṉe Pédrona' chi'e:
Na'ch beṉ'ka' nak Jesúza' txen wbig'gake' kwite'na', gollgake'ne':
Na' beṉ' zan bllin lawe'na' nc̱he'gake' no beṉ' bi chak sa', no beṉ' lc̱hoḻ, no beṉ' bi chak iṉe, no beṉ' nxiṉj, no beṉ' chak bichlə yillwe'. Na' bzoagake' ḻegake' lao Jesúza' na' biyone' ḻegake'.
¿Bic̱he c̱he yetxtila'lə wyajnizile ka wnia' wsak'gale c̱he levadura c̱he fariseoka' len saduceoka'?
―X̱an', ḻe mbalaz zoacho ni. Shi cheenilo', gon' shoṉ ransh, ton cho', ston c̱he Moiséza' na' ston c̱he Elíaza'.
Na' ka billin Jesúza' len beṉ'ka' nakgake'ne' txen Capernaúma', beṉ' Israelka' beṉ'ka' chc̱hixj c̱he yoodo'na' jawiagake' Pédrona', na' wṉabgakile'ne':
’Na' dii ḻi nia' le', diika' iṉale bi gon beṉ' yell-lioni, ḻekzka' iṉa Chioza' zoa yabana', na' diika' iṉale wak gon beṉ' yell-lioni, ḻekzka' iṉa Chioza' zoa yabana'.
―Na' ¿bic̱he ben dii Moiséza' mandad kat' to beṉ' yiḻaa xoole'na' chiyaḻ' wḻise' to yish dii we'n dill' bich nake' xoole' na' wak yichooṉe'ne'?
Na' bibangakile' ka wne', na' che' ljwellgake':
Na' gongake' nad' lo na' beṉ'ka' bi nak beṉ' Israel kwenc̱he wtitjgakile' nad' na' wit c̱hingake' nad', na'tech wda'gake' nad' ḻee yag cruza', per ka gak shoṉ lla yiban' ladj beṉ' wetka'.
―Ḻi shaj yella' daa llia shḻaana'. Na' ile'ile to burr ba noolə da'b yag na' nc̱he' to xiiṉdo'b. Na' wsell-leb wc̱he'legakb nilə.
―¡Batch kwio' yix̱wewa'!
’Na'tech bene'n lo na' to c̱hop beṉ' na' wzee zeje' zit'.
Na'ch wza' wen llinka' zejgake', na' jx̱i'gake' kon no beṉ' billaggake', ka beṉ' wen ka beṉ' mal. Na' billa'cha lill beṉ' wṉabia'na'.
“Nad nak' Chios c̱he Abrahama', Isaaca' na' Jacoba'”? Na' bi nake' Chios c̱he beṉ' wet, san nake' Chios c̱he beṉ' ban, ḻa' lao Chioza' mban beṉ'ki.
Na' kono ye'le “x̱a” lo yell-lioni, ḻa' toz Chioza', beena' zoa yabana', nake' X̱ale.
Na' nia' le', bich ile'ile nad' ax̱t kat'ch illin lla iṉale: “¡Gaklenshga X̱ancho Chioza' beeni ba bseḻee!”
Ḻa' kat' nad', Beṉ' Bseḻ' Chioza' Yell-lioni, zizaa dii yoblə, gak ka chak kat' chep yes na' chzeeni'n doxen xan yabana'.
Na' do ka chel besyaa to beṉ', chi'e: “¡Ba za' bi' wishagna'na', ḻi sho' lljatilchob'!”
Ḻa' ka wdon', bwaole nad'; na' ka wbiḻid', beṉle dii weej'; na' ka wda' ka beṉ' zit', bleble nad' lill-lena'.
―¿Ka'k' c̱hixjle nad' shi gon' Jesúza' lo na'le?
Na'ch che' Pédrona'ne':
―Bish'dawaa, ben daa zidyeno'.
―Shi lin' Crístona', wnashki non wdap wlall' li'.
―¿Alin' beṉ' wṉabia' c̱he beṉ' Israelka'?
Na'ch bisan Pilátona' Barrabáza', na' bene' mandad bet wdingake' Jesúza' na' bene'ne' lo na'gake' kwenc̱he wda'gake'ne' ḻee yag cruza'.
Na' ka wite', lechaa ze ḻoo yoodo'na' lii bchez'ten gokan c̱hoplə. Na' gok to bedxo' na' wlaa yajka'.
―Bi illeble. Ḻi lljayell beṉ' bishaaka' shajgake' Galileana' na' ile'gakile' nad' na'.
Na' wzoe' na' c̱hoa lla ladj ba zṉiaka', na' Satanáza' daa chṉabia' dii x̱iw'ka' goklalliin kooyeḻa'n ḻe' gone' ka cheenin. Na' ka wde, jaklen anjlka' ḻe'.
Na' che' Jesúza' ḻegake':
Na' wzolla' Levína' janoe'ne'.
―Bḻi noona'.
Na'ch bllin xṉa' Jesúza' len beṉ' bisheeka', wzegake' lesh' chyoona' na' bseḻ'gake' beṉ' jaṉegake'ne'.
Na' zoa zi baḻ beṉ' chengakile' cho'a xtill' Chioza' na' chajḻe'gake' do yic̱hj do lall'gake', na' chon xshinin ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'eka'. Na' chak c̱hegake' ka biṉna' bxop lo yo wenna' daa wllia shichoa wej, na' guiyon wej na'ch to guiyoa wej.
Na' ḻe bllebgake', na' che' ljwellgake':
Na' bllin to beṉ' le Jairo, nake' to beṉ'ka' chgoogake' xṉezi diika' chon beṉ' Israelka' gana' chdop chllaggake' choe'ḻwillgake' Chioza'. Na' ka blline' gana' ze Jesúza', bc̱hek' xibe' lawe'na'
Na' biza' Jesúza' biyaje' lalle'na', na' beṉ'ka' nakgake'ne' txen zejlengake'ne'.
Per ka wyayi Heródeza' yiz, bene' to lṉi na' goxe' beṉ'ka' chṉabia', na' x̱an soldadka', na' beṉ'ka' mbejlawin gana' mbani Galileana'. Na' got' xḻatjin gon Herodíaza' ka cheenile'.
Na' ka wṉezgakile' ka'ka'n de, na' che'gake'ne':
na' aga choe'la'ogake' nad' do yic̱hj do lall'gake'.
―Lekzilo'n, beṉ'do', per bekw'ka' chbe'gakb xan mesa' na' chitopgakb bḻaaka' chxop.
Na' bizee kwite'ka', na' biyo'e ḻoo barkwa' sto shii ziyaje' shḻaa nisdo'na'.
Na' che' Pédrona':
Na' nia' le', ba biyed Elíaza', na' bengakile'ne' daa nazan c̱hegake', kon ka na Cho'a Xtill' Chioza' gongake' c̱he'.
―Nad', Beṉ' Bseḻ' Chioza' Yell-lioni, gon beṉ' nad' lo na' beṉ' malka' na' witgake' nad', na' ka gak shoṉ lla, yiban' ladj beṉ' wetka'.
Na' che' Jesúza' ḻegake':
Ka bengakile' golle' ka', zizikli bibangakile', na' che' ljwellgake':
Per aga kan' chiyaḻ' gonle. Shi nole cheenile gakle beṉ' mbejlawin chiyaḻ' gon kwinle ka wen llin c̱he beṉ'.
Na' ka beṉ'ka' llialo lao Jesúza' ka beṉ'ka' nogake'ne', chosyaagake', nagake':
Na'ch choe'len ljwellgake' dill', che'gake':
Na' be'gake'ne'n, na' che' Jesúza' ḻegake':
Na' shlak chli' chsedi Jesúza' beṉ'ka' lesh' chyoodo'na', na' chi'e ḻegake':
Na' kat' ba zjwa'gake' le' lao beṉ'ka' chṉabia', bi sele wṉeyi bin ye'le ḻegake', san daa wzajnii Chioza' len' iṉele, ḻa' aga tobia'lall'zlen iṉele, san Espíritu Sántonan' iṉe.
Ka zoa Jesúza' Betániana', wyaje' lill beena' le Simón, beena' gok yillwe' daa le lepra. Na' shlak chi'e cho'a mesa', bllin to noolə nox̱ee to lmet de yaj xochi yoollan set zix̱ de nardo na' dii xen zakaan. Na' wdishje' yen lmeta' na' bwazje' set zix̱a' yic̱hj Jesúza'.
Na' chi'e ḻegake':
Ni choe'te Jesúza' dill' ka bllin Juda', beena' wlen beṉ'ka' shlliṉ, lene' beṉ' zan beṉ'ka' bseḻ' bx̱ozka' chṉabia' len beṉ'ka' chli' chsedi leya' na'ch beṉ' golka' chṉabia', nox̱'gake' spad, na' no yag.
Na' yog'ḻoḻgake' bc̱hoglogake' c̱he' nan chiyaḻ' guete'.
― ¿Acheenile yisan' beṉ' wṉabia' c̱heleni, le' nakle beṉ' Israel?
―Beṉ' yoblə gok bisle', na' bi chak yisla kwine'.
Ḻi yiyaj lao beṉ'ka' nakgake'ne' txen na' len lao Pédrona', na' ḻi lljayellgake': “Ba ziyaje' zjaleze' le' Galileana', na' na' yile'ile'ne' sto shii, kon ka wne' le'.”
ḻa' xiiṉo'na' gakb' to beṉ' zakii lao Chioza'. Bi chiyaḻ' wnix̱b' vino wa bichlə dii gonan ka sollib', na' Espíritu Sántona' soloe' iṉabi'e yic̱hjlall'do'baa ka zi' galjləb'.
―Xmos X̱ancho Chiozan' nak', na' wak gone' c̱ha' kon ka ba wno'.
Na'ch ka wṉezi beṉ' wlill c̱he'ka' na' beṉ' dialla c̱he'ka', wyajgake' bibalengakile'ne' daa ba biyeshii X̱ancho Chioza' ḻe'.
kwenc̱he yizi'xen Chioza' saaxya c̱he'ka' na' yisle' ḻegake' bi tegake' lo yeḻ' zak'zi'na'.
Na' kon ka na ley c̱he dii Moiséza' gongake', wlezgake' ka bzaa llaka' bixi biyech Maríana' len bdo' c̱he'na', na'ch wyajlengake'b' Jerusalénna' kwenc̱he jengake'b' lo na' X̱ancho Chioza'.
―Xiiṉdawaa, ¿bic̱he benzilo' neto' ka'? X̱o'ni na' nad' ba gokshejlall'chgainto' biyiljnto' li'.
Na' ḻekzka' baḻ beṉ'ka' nak soldad wṉabgakile'ne':
Ka biza' Jesúza' cho'a yao Jordanna', Espíritu Sántona', beena' chṉabia' ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'ena', bc̱hi'ene' latja' gana' bibi chashj chḻeb.
na' gaklen' beṉ'ka' chc̱hi' chsak' beṉ' ḻegake',
Na' bibeje' dii x̱iwaa yoo beṉ' zan, na' ka bichejgakan chosyaagakan zillj inlleb, che'gakan:
Per Jesúza' yooloe' chaje' ga kono beṉ' chak kwenc̱he chjeḻwille' Chioza'.
Na' ḻekzka' bzoe' sto jempl, chi'e ḻegake':
Wyajgake' kwit Jesúza' kwenc̱he wzenaggake' xtilleena' na' yiyakgakile' bi yillwe' dii chakgake'. Na' ḻekzka' biyaki beṉ'ka' chsak'zi' dii x̱iw'ka' ḻegake'.
Ka ile'icho daa chbia to yag, na' chṉezicho bi yag daa. Yag yeshaa aga wbian yix̱wewa', na' ḻekzka' yag bisgaana' aga wbian uvana'.
Na' doxen gana' mbani Judeana' na' yellka' llia gaozə wṉezgakile' daa ben Jesúza'.
―Simón, de to dii cheenid' iṉia' li'.
―Le' chenile dga nia', ḻi sen wṉeyi.
Na' ka ble'ile' Jesúza', besyee na' jac̱hek' xibe' lawe'na', na' zillj inlleb chi'e:
Na'ch goll Jesúza'ne':
Na' che' Jesúza' ḻegake':
Na' Pédrona' len Juanna' na' Jacóbona' ḻe chakxwesgake', per bendiplall'gake' bi wtesgake', na'ch ble'gakile' yeḻ' chey cheeni' c̱he Jesúza' na' c̱he beṉ'ka' zi c̱hop bllin kwite'na'.
Na' beṉ' Samáriaka' bi blebgake'ne' daa ṉezgakile' Jerusalénna'lan yiyaje'.
Na' yiyonle beṉ'ka' bi shao' yella', na' ye'le ḻegake': “Yeḻ' wṉabia' c̱he Chioza' ba bla'n laoleni.”
―¿Noran bish' ljwell'?
Bi we'gacho' latj ibix̱nto' gonnto' daa bi nak wen, san bislagach neto' lo ṉi'a na' dii mala'.
Na' bdi'a bllagch beṉ'ka' kwit Jesúza' na' golle' ḻegake':
goklall'gake' we' Jesúza' dill' dii wchix̱a'n ḻe'.
Ḻi wwiakachi bec̱hjka', ḻa'kzi bi chaz chaaṉgakb na' bibi chizi' chilapgakb, ni bi zoa ga chgooshao'gakb dii gaogakb, len chweej chwaokz Chioza' ḻegakb. Na' le', ṉaa, zak'techle aga ka bado'ka' ze lo llazə.
Ḻa' ṉaa, shi to yoo lle' gayee, na' gakgake' c̱hoplə, shoṉe' tiḻ-lengake' beṉ'ka' c̱hop, na' beṉ'ka' zi c̱hop tiḻ-lengake' beṉ'ka' zi shoṉə.
Na' ka goll Jesúza' ka', yog' beṉ'ka' chakzbangakile'ne' biyii bido'gakile', na' yog' beṉ'ka' sto bibagakile' daa ble'gakile' yeḻ' wakka' chone'.
―Wak yiyajo'.
Na' iṉagake': “Kon wdishj beena' len yoona' na' bi goki xmeche'na' wzeeloe'n.”
Na' x̱abaa chi'e wen llin c̱he'ka': “Ḻobe'zə ḻi lljḻej tgot lech' daa ḻiizelozi nakch na' ḻi wwakwba'n, na' ḻekzka' ḻi wllin to niy xbemaa na' ḻi wllin yel ṉi'abaa.
’Dii ḻi nia' le', ḻobe'ch te c̱he yabana' len yell-lioni, aga ka daa tegonz shc̱ho'a daa na leya'.
Na' shlak zjada Jesúza' Jerusalénna', wdie' gana' ndiḻ yell-lioka' mbani Samáriana' na' Galileana'.
’Na' nia' le', lle'na' kat' zizaa, c̱hop beṉ' die' toz blag, toe' yic̱hi'a na' stoe' yigaaṉ.
―¿Berac̱he nazo' nad' beṉ' wen? Toz Chioza' nake' beṉ' wen.
Na' beṉ'ka' llialo lao Jesúza' chsheshlengake'ne' kwenc̱he kwi'e llizə, na' zizikchlə chosyee, chi'e:
Na'ch beṉ' wṉabia'na' chi'ene': “Wenkzan beno'. Daa beno' ka chiyaḻ' kon lat' mecha' bkwaaṉlen' li', wzoa' li' iṉabi'o shi yell.”
Na' ka billine' gaozə yell Jerusalénna', gokyeshile' ka ble'ile'n na' wchelle' c̱he beṉ'ka' zoa na'.
Na' wlejgake'b' gana' lle' yag uvaka' na' betgake'b'.
Na'ch che' Jesúza' ḻegake':
Na' ka yenile chak no wdiḻ wa chtop chshag ljwell beṉ' kwenc̱he soshyi'gake' beṉ' wṉabia'ka', bi illeble. Chonan byen zigaate gak diiki, per aga lii tete c̱he yell-lioni kat' ba chakgakan.
Na' Jesúza' bli' bsedile' beṉ' yog' lla yoodo'na', na' ka chaḻ, chjagaaṉe' lo Yaa Olívoza'.
Ḻa' ba bllin lla gak ka nak daa llia bia' gak c̱ha', nad', Beṉ' Bseḻ' Chioza' Yell-lioni, per ¡nyesh'laz gak c̱he beena' gone' nad' lo na' beṉ' malka'!
―Ḻi we'ḻwill Chioza' kwenc̱he bi we'zle latj gon beli chenna' le' gan.
―Bi len' nak' beṉ'ka' txen.
―Kan' nakan.
Na' beṉ' zan zjanogake'ne', na' zan noolka' chbellgake' na' chosyaagake' ni c̱he Jesúza'.
Na' biyoll golle' ka' na'ch wite'.
―¿Bera dillaan choe'le za'le ni? ¿Berac̱he chakyesh'zile?
Na' ḻe bllebgake' daa chakgakile' yel bx̱enzan chwiagake'.
Na' beena' nsa' beeni'na' bidsoe' yell-lioni, na' ḻa'kzi ḻe' bx̱e bsile' yell-lioni, beṉ'ka' lle' lawinna' aga gokbe'gakile' non nake'.
na' ḻen' zi' wli'lawe'. Na' nad' ni bi zakaa gak' xmose' kwenc̱he galj' ḻa'c̱h' xele'na'.
Na'ch jadilj Felípena' Natanaela' na' chi'ene':
Na'ch che' Jesúza' ḻegake':
Na' che' Nicodémona'ne':
Kwinkzle benile kana' wnia' aga nadaan Crístona', beena' chbezcho wseḻ' Chioza', san nak' to beṉ' bseḻee kwenc̱he kwialoa' lawe'na' na' yep' beṉ' wzenaggake' c̱he'.
Na' che' Jesúza'ne':
―Yeḻ' wao c̱ha'na' nakan daa chon' ka cheeni beena' bseḻ' nad' na' wzeeloa' daa cheenile' gon'.
Na' ḻoo koridorka' de beṉ' zan beṉ' we', no beṉ' lc̱hoḻ, no beṉ' bi chak sa' wen, na' no beṉ' net ṉi'a nee, chbezgake' ta nisa'.
’Dii ḻi nia' le', beena' chzenag xtillaana' na' chonḻilallee beena' bseḻ' nad', gat' yeḻ' mban c̱he' zejḻi kaṉi. Na' aga bi de dii gonan ka c̱hoglo c̱he' sak'zi'e, san ba bile' lo yeḻ' wita' na' ba zoe' lo yeḻ' mban daa bi te c̱heyin.
Golle' ka' daa chakile' la'shki bi yee Felípena', ḻa' ba ṉezkzile' nakan gone'.
Na' che'gake'ne':
